user.name: Emilio Jesús Gallego Arias
user.bio: “La perfection est atteinte, non pas lorsqu'il n'y a plus rien à ajouter, mais lorsqu'il n'y a plus rien à retirer.”

commit.title: Remove declare_object for SsrHave NoTCResolution.
commit.message:
Remove declare_object for SsrHave NoTCResolution.

IIUC, this was a hack to make `Set SsrHave NoTCResolution` behave like
`Global Set SsrHave NoTCResolution`. I don't think it is needed (just
let the user write the desired locality), but if it is, the right way of
doing it is to let clients of Goptions specify a default locality.
